org.openlca.core.results

Class ContributionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openlca.core.results.BaseResult
      • org.openlca.core.results.SimpleResult
        • org.openlca.core.results.ContributionResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FullResult

    public class ContributionResult
extends SimpleResult
    A contribution result extends a simple result and contains all single contributions of processes and products to the overall inventory and impact assessment results. Additionally, it contains the contributions of the single inventory flows to impact category results.
